textBeforeTable: The Druid's Deep is a Forgotten Realms adventure pack introduced with Update 15. It includes 4 quests. These are level 17 on heroic difficulty and level 23 on epic difficulty. The NPC contact persons that bestow the quests are located in the north-eastern part of Eveningstar. Fight a strange corruption of nature that has come out of the King's Forest to threaten Eveningstar. Unravel the mystery of its cause in a tale that introduces new allies, new enemies, and troubling riddles that can only be answered down in the very heart of Druid's Deep. : The Druid's Deep A list of all adventure packs Definition: adventure pack Requires access to adventure pack searchnavigation , Jump to:
textAfterTable: * The Druid's Curse requires flagging to be bestowed. After completing all four quests, Anazar Narroun will offer you three of any type Commendation, ML15 version of the items that can drop in the quests, or a Guild Renown. This chain can be repeated to earn the chain end reward again.
